hopobject.body: I've got a full-time job levitra professional 20 mg If you're worried about a pension, the key figure to watchis your plan's funded status - that is, the percentage of assetson hand to pay promised benefits. Actuaries generally use 80percent as a floor for safe funding levels. But the figuresdepend heavily on the assumptions by fund managers on theirexpected rate of return on portfolios over time. And thoseassumptions have become very controversial.
